{"tid":2285640,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼滅之刃 1-26集，睇【無限列車】前重溫一下 (請勿劇透)","createTime":"2020-11-14T09:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T13:36:18.000Z","uid":265458,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a769cbf2fe255ae48b3dd93996aae5fa1debd2","tid":2285640,"uid":265458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"鬼滅之刃 1-26集<br />\n<a href=\"https://flymovie.top/index.php/vod/detail/id/18112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflymovie.top%2Findex.php%2Fvod%2Fdetail%2Fid%2F18112&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=caf90c73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://flymovie.top/index.php/vod/detail/id/18112</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ikuma.cc/wp-content/uploads/flickr/50264978082_99d33410fd_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fikuma.cc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fflickr%2F50264978082_99d33410fd_c.jpg&h=7dadd29e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n大正時代，竈門炭治郎繼承亡父留下的炭業工作，支撐一家七口，在山上過著樸實的生活。某日他做完生意返家後發現全家遭鬼王鬼舞辻無慘屠殺，而大妹禰豆子變成了鬼。鬼殺隊富岡義勇見狀後本欲斬殺禰豆子，但他在見識到兄妹倆的親情後，推薦炭治郎拜鱗瀧左近次為師。炭治郎經過兩年訓練，學會對抗鬼的呼吸法與劍術，通過考驗加入鬼殺隊。<br />\n<br />\n故事設定<br />\n平安時代罹患絕症的青年無慘在受到治療後成為了「鬼」，雖具有超長壽命和強悍的身體能力，卻必須以人為食，且有受日曬會死亡及接觸紫藤花會中毒的弱點。無慘希望找到克服陽光的方法，便製造許多手下，旗下實力最強大的十二隻鬼會被授予「十二鬼月」的稱號，強大的鬼可使用異能「血鬼術」。"},{"pid":"c2d62fcc47357c54abd3b023ed86671e80cef297","tid":2285640,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:44:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/137208/%E9%AC%BC%E6%BB%85%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.com%2Fott%2Fhk%2Fzh-hk%2Fvod%2F137208%2F%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E6%25BB%2585%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2588%2583&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=09f41378\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/zh-hk/vod/137208/%E9%AC%BC%E6%BB%85%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%83</a>"},{"pid":"e2dfa92e770150281de11a56025403f25fa47e6e","tid":2285640,"uid":200529,"